text: Semyon Babintsev (born October 8, 1994) is a Russian professional ice hockey right winger who is currently playing for ORG Beijing of the Supreme Hockey League (VHL). ==Career== Babintsev played three seasons at junior level with the Mississauga Steelheads of the Ontario Hockey League before joining Nomad Astana of the Kazakhstan Hockey Championship in 2015. In the 2016-17 season, Babintsev played in the Kontinental Hockey League for HC SochiПопов в «Ак Барсе» и другие трансферные новости 1 июня (in Russian) and in the Czech Extraliga for HC Litvínov.Babintsev za Litvínov (in Czech) After a spell with Sokol Krasnoyarsk of the Supreme Hockey League, Babintsev signed for the Utah Grizzlies of the ECHL on February 13, 2018. On August 14, 2018, Babintsev signed with ECHL expansion team the Newfoundland Growlers.Growlers agree to terms with Babintsev He was released from the team on March 11, 2019.ECHL Transactions - March 11 ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:HC Litvínov players Category:Mississauga Steelheads players Category:HC Most players Category:Newfoundland Growlers players Category:Nomad Astana players Category:Russian ice hockey right wingers Category:HC Sochi players Category:Sokol Krasnoyarsk players Category:Sportspeople from Moscow Category:Utah Grizzlies (ECHL) players
